{
  "page": "A Game of Thrones-Chapter 10",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(2, 126, 177)\">Jon II</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\"><img alt=\"AGameOfThrones.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/93/AGameOfThrones.jpg/220px-AGameOfThrones.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"335\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/93/AGameOfThrones.jpg/330px-AGameOfThrones.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/93/AGameOfThrones.jpg/440px-AGameOfThrones.jpg 2x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n77 <small>US HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(2, 126, 177)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_5\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 5\">Jon I</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 9\">Tyrion I</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jon II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 11\">Daenerys II</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 19\">Jon III</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a> says his last goodbyes, first to the comatose <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a>, then to <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb</a>, and finally to <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a>, to whom he gives a <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a>-type <a href=\"/index.php/Needle\" title=\"Needle\">sword</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_10&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a> climbs the stairs to <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a>'s room with <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">Ghost</a> beside him, fearing that it might be the last time. <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn</a> is there, having never left Bran's side for close to a fortnight, which has kept Jon away, but now there is no more time. When Jon enters, Catelyn responds with hostility, asking why he is here and demanding he leave. While once this would have sent him crying, now it only makes Jon angry so that when Catelyn threatens to call <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark_guards\" title=\"House Stark guards\">the guards</a>, he calls her bluff. \n</p><p>Jon finds Bran emaciated and shrunken, and the covers over his legs look wrong. Jon asks Bran not to die and tells him everyone is waiting for him to wake up. Jon remembers how much Bran was looking forward to the journey south while explaining that he is going north to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> with Uncle <a href=\"/index.php/Benjen_Stark\" title=\"Benjen Stark\">Benjen</a>. Catelyn admits that she was wishing for Bran to stay home with her, and her wish seems to have been granted. When Jon attempts to reassure her, she lashes out at him and, as he is leaving, tells him that it should have been him that fell.\n</p><p>Jon makes the long walk to the yard, where things are in an uproar as the party prepares to leave. <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb</a> brings news that Benjen is looking for Jon. When Robb asks about his mother, Jon tells him she was kind. Robb then remarks that next time they meet, Jon will be all in black, and they hug farewell. \n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lucas_Durham_Aryas_gift.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Lucas_Durham_Aryas_gift.jpg/250px-Lucas_Durham_Aryas_gift.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Lucas_Durham_Aryas_gift.jpg/375px-Lucas_Durham_Aryas_gift.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Lucas_Durham_Aryas_gift.jpg/500px-Lucas_Durham_Aryas_gift.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lucas_Durham_Aryas_gift.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jon gives <a href=\"/index.php/Needle\" title=\"Needle\">Needle</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Arya\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arya\">Arya</a>. Art by Lucas Durham © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Next, Jon goes to the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Keep_of_Winterfell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Great Keep of Winterfell\">Great Keep</a> to see <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a>, who is repacking her things with help from <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a>, not having folded them well enough for Septa <a href=\"/index.php/Mordane\" title=\"Mordane\">Mordane</a> the first time. Jon says he has a secret present for her. After Arya closes the door and sets Nymeria to guard it, Jon gives her a small sword made specially for her, one like the swords from <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>. He explains to her that she will have to practise every day, shows her how to hold it, and then gives her her first lesson: stick them with the pointy end. He then warns her not to tell <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a>. Arya runs to him for a last hug. Just before he leaves, Jon tells Arya that all the best swords have a name. When she asks what her sword's name is, he explains that it is her very favorite thing. They then say the name together: \"<a href=\"/index.php/Needle\" title=\"Needle\">Needle</a>\".\n</p>\n<div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_list\">Character list</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_10&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character list\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:50%;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">Ghost</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Wind\" title=\"Grey Wind\">Grey Wind</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria_(direwolf)\" title=\"Nymeria (direwolf)\">Nymeria</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a></li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:50%;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Benjen_Stark\" title=\"Benjen Stark\">Benjen Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mikken\" title=\"Mikken\">Mikken</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mordane\" title=\"Mordane\">Mordane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Summer\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mentions\">Mentions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_10&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Mentions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Houses:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Places:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Great_Keep_of_Winterfell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Great Keep of Winterfell\">Great Keep of Winterfell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Catelyn%27s_sept\" title=\"Lady Catelyn&#39;s sept\">Lady Catelyn's sept</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:50;\">\n<p><b>Terms:</b>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">Bastard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bravo\" title=\"Bravo\">Bravo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">Direwolf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark_guards\" title=\"House Stark guards\">House Stark guards</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ironwood\" title=\"Ironwood\">Ironwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Needle\" title=\"Needle\">Needle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">Septa</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Southron\" title=\"Southron\">Southron</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sworn_Brother\" title=\"Sworn Brother\">Sworn Brother</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_10&amp;action=edit&am